{"tid":2204302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"檢測支援隊離港　藍屍持感謝卡到機場欲送行被拒","createTime":"2020-09-16T03:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T04:42:56.000Z","uid":6497,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebe1e4d4650a9ca47b4e301e459744d3bba5897","tid":2204302,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200916/s00001/cfac0c1bc29a7bb6daa16c068ce86a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200916%2Fs00001%2Fcfac0c1bc29a7bb6daa16c068ce86a52.jpg&h=c3ee107f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200916/s00001/1600224096408/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200916%2Fs00001%2F1600224096408%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=c45cfb46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200916%2Fs00001%2F1600224096408%2F&h=d4a657ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200916/s00001/1600224096408/</a><br />\n<br />\n為期14日的普及社區檢測（全民檢測）前日（14日）結束，內地核酸檢測支援隊今日（16日）離港。今早8時31分，一名女子手持感謝卡到機場，稱欲進入機場客運大樓，向500多名今日離港的內地核酸檢測支援隊隊員表達謝意及送行，惟因未持登機證明文件被保安截停，其間雙方一度起爭執及有人報警，及後該女子自行離去。<br />\n<br />\n因應去年反修例運動，機場自去年8月起實施人流管制，僅容許持有24小時內離港機票或登機證，以及有效旅遊證件的離境旅客，或持有相關證件的機場員工，方可進入客運大樓範圍。"},{"pid":"5edab4061ff67b5924376652bc96b7ed1a343804","tid":2204302,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"早幾個星期無人check<br />\n依家又check返？"},{"pid":"ed1a51f2c620cce08a0661d6b7e7d4880dad0e12","tid":2204302,"uid":143230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"沉默的大多數=1"},{"pid":"7639207a370d0772656991de0d264fad1574118c","tid":2204302,"uid":239392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"一人送別，慘過送殯"},{"pid":"a742db5fffc9b6e5751b8664874309c5fbe11a56","tid":2204302,"uid":18251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"1人真心on9膠"},{"pid":"0889126b47c67ecb8d8ea195c600e73390695313","tid":2204302,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"送演員走"},{"pid":"1ed4c3e3f0b62d8c555505931f8d0094e31c112a","tid":2204302,"uid":331739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"藍絲：太遠了 搭車入去都幾十蚊 我哋精神上送別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f3ba9617f5419559298e3f1acd6252d425ce76","tid":2204302,"uid":244034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ed4c3e3f0b62d8c555505931f8d0094e31c112a","tid":2204302,"uid":331739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"藍絲：太遠了 搭車入去都幾十蚊 我哋精神上送別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"影唔到相冇錢收仲泄車錢"},{"pid":"724ac10e7416567d7111429fdd9eb57ef6c01956","tid":2204302,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"沉默的大多數&gt;繼續沉默"},{"pid":"80aa52a53e1e5b87da1675d8d47ead8ae88a1868","tid":2204302,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"香港機場拍烏繩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞埋D咩禁制令 on99"},{"pid":"858fe0b6655ab8cfbada10125cddf7c53789577d","tid":2204302,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0302c126f43cbf438a5d5c0513be71e6d579ec50","tid":2204302,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"係咪藍屍網上CALL馬最後得一條友到場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689f518067bec257205e09149c751009fbf2c643","tid":2204302,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80aa52a53e1e5b87da1675d8d47ead8ae88a1868","tid":2204302,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"香港機場拍烏繩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞埋D咩禁制令 on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"日頭仲靜過正常時期既凌晨三四點"},{"pid":"442e00264c1cfab7eebcfa23b1f53c264fb3a902","tid":2204302,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nATHtin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnATHtin.png&h=968b170c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果醬便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「幾千不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;幾千！&hellip;&hellip;幾千蚊的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「自食其力」，什麼「龍粉」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</blockquote>好撚顛係咁屌太古街坊窮閪<br />\n仆街人地酒樓有平價車隊送<br />\n你水人加幾十元隻找你送喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔係水人加幾十蚊<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">根據琴日睇太古人個page cap圖係<br />\n每樣野$30運費 即係片皮鴨$30 叫隻雞$30 炒碟菜$30 <br />\n片皮鴨個二食$10 <br />\n即係咁樣叫要俾$100運費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於酒樓本來個運費係 全部order 裝得上酒樓架車既都係$300包車<br />\n總之你愈多人叫 咪愈平 因為平均分擔個$300</blockquote>仆街 逐樣計 咁大生意都比佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8301da56df36e6e8089047a85c3a9feb5622e89b","tid":2204302,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"一千人，有畫面，有政治宣傳效果，批准！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一條友？冇畫面！冇利用價值，死開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eca47de7eb2fc8ea6686acce4ce9533214ba729","tid":2204302,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689f518067bec257205e09149c751009fbf2c643","tid":2204302,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8